FBIS3-57972 "drweu003__a94033" FBIS-WEU-94-003-A Document Type:Daily Report 5 January 1994 ANNEX Italy & Vatican City 1994 Deficit Pegged at Almost 142 Trillion Lire BR3012125393 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1216 GMT 30 Dec 93--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR3012125393 Rome ANSAMAIL Database Language: English Article Type:BFN [Unattributed article: "Forecast Deficit at 142 Trillion"] [Text] Rome, 30 Dec (ANSA) -- The 1994 Budget and Finance Bill, approved by parliament last week and published Thursday [30 December] in the Official Gazette, nails the deficit for next year at 141.97 trillion lire (83.51 billion dollars). The state will not be allowed to obtain more than 294.7 trillion lire (173.3 billion dollars) through the financial markets, according to the bill.
